    <published>2017-04-16T15:16:35.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-04-16T15:33:44.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Git-Page로-빠르게-Hosting-하기"><a href="#Git-Page로-빠르게-Hosting-하기" class="headerlink" title="Git Page로 빠르게 Hosting 하기"></a>Git Page로 빠르게 Hosting 하기</h2><h3 id="Github-Repository-생성하기"><a href="#Github-Repository-생성하기" class="headerlink" title="Github Repository 생성하기"></a>Github Repository 생성하기</h3><ul>
<li>[x] + New Repository</li>
<li>[x] Repository 이름은 USERNAME.github.io</li>
<li>[x] Public / Private 중 Public 선택</li>
<li>[x] Initialize this repository with a README을 체크한다</li>
<li>[x] 마지막으로 Create Repository 버튼을 통해 Repository 생성</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="Github-Page-설정"><a href="#Github-Page-설정" class="headerlink" title="Github Page 설정"></a>Github Page 설정</h3><ul>
<li>[x] Settings &gt; Options &gt; Github Pages 메뉴로 이동</li>
<li>[x] Theme chooser 메뉴에서 Change Theme 선택</li>
<li>[x] 원하는 Theme를 선택하고 README.md 파일을 Commit 한다</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="USERNAME-github-io-접속"><a href="#USERNAME-github-io-접속" class="headerlink" title="USERNAME.github.io 접속"></a>USERNAME.github.io 접속</h3><ul>
<li>[x] 정상적으로 Git Page에 접속되는지 확인</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="Hexo"><a href="#Hexo" class="headerlink" title="Hexo"></a>Hexo</h2><blockquote>
<p><a href="https://hexo.io/" target="_blank" rel="external">https://hexo.io/</a><br><a href="https://github.com/pinggod/hexo-theme-apollo" target="_blank" rel="external">https://github.com/pinggod/hexo-theme-apollo</a></p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="Requirements"><a href="#Requirements" class="headerlink" title="Requirements"></a>Requirements</h3><h3 id="Write-Post"><a href="#Write-Post" class="headerlink" title="Write Post"></a>Write Post</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">hexo new post [post_name]</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="Test-Locally"><a href="#Test-Locally" class="headerlink" title="Test Locally"></a>Test Locally</h3><p>아래의 Command를 통해 서버가 구동되면 <a href="http://localhost:4000" target="_blank" rel="external">http://localhost:4000</a> 을 통해 로컬 브라우저에서 블로그에 접속 할 수 있습니다.<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">hexo server</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h3 id="Deploy"><a href="#Deploy" class="headerlink" title="Deploy"></a>Deploy</h3><p>Hexo는 Git Page를 통해 손쉽게 배포가 가능합니다.</p>
<p><strong>Update _config.yml</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment"># Deployment</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">## Docs: https://hexo.io/docs/deployment.html</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">deploy:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  type:</span> <span class="string">git</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  repo:</span> <span class="attr">https://github.com/&#123;USERNAME&#125;/&#123;USERNAME&#125;.github.io</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><strong>Terminal에서 Command를 통해 배포합니다</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">hexo deploy --generate</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="Themes"><a href="#Themes" class="headerlink" title="Themes"></a>Themes</h2><p><a href="https://hexo.io/themes/" target="_blank" rel="external">https://hexo.io/themes/</a></p>
<p><strong>Update _config.yml</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="attr">theme:</span> <span class="string">apollo</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">hexo clean</div><div class="line">hexo deploy --generate</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
    
